comments: Jones (NOP) adjusts his path and some marginal contact occurs during Hampton's (ORL) drives that does not affect his SQBR.
Valanciunas (NOP) gets to ball height and makes direct contact with the ball that dislodges it during Harris' (ORL) driving shot attempt at the basket.
Okeke (ORL) cuts into the paint and Jones (NOP) brings an arm to the offensive players hip but slides it off and the brief marginal contact has no impact on Okeke's FOM.
Wagner (ORL) gathers on his right foot, establishing his left foot as his pivot, which he maintains before releasing his shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) brings his arm down and makes more than marginal contact with the left arm and shoulder of Wagner (ORL) that affects the shot attempt at the basket.
McCollum (NOP) drives to the basket and momentarily extends and retracts his off-arm to and from the midsection of M. Wagner (ORL). The marginal touch does not impact the defensive player's play.
McCollum (NOP) makes marginal contact with Okeke's (ORL) midsection, which he is able to move through and maintain control of the ball.
Alvarado (NOP) reaches in and makes contact with Harris' (ORL) wrist after his gather, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Hampton (ORL).
Hampton (ORL) reaches in and makes contact with the wrist and arm of Valanciunas (NOP), which causes him to bobble the ball prior to the start of his dribble.
Orlando is not able to advance the ball into the frontcourt before eight seconds had passed on the shot clock.
McCollum (NOP) and Harris (ORL) engage and disengage during the inbound play.
McCollum (NOP) maintains a legal pivot foot during his step back move into his shot attempt.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Okeke (ORL).
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hampton (ORL) and some contact occurs as he firms up on the screen but said contact is only marginal.
Alvarado (NOP) commits a take foul on Ross (ORL).
Valanciunas (NOP) does not establish himself in Hampton's (ORL) path when leg contact occurs on the pick.
Snell (NOP) commits a take foul on Okeke (ORL).
